::Hakibuscon::

	Hakibuscon stood still for a second as he stared at the angry Dinobot. 
Wow, this guy seemed serious.  But strangely, the bot, Hakibuscon's sensors
read Dinobot and the other was Tavatron, had some compassion in the form of
anger and hatred.  There was no way this bot could have been a Predacon. 
But he had the looks!  Why was he giving me a chance, Hakibuscon thought.

	"Why are you giving me a chance to leave?  Why are you enjoying this
place?  You don't seem like the Predacons I have been spying on the past
few years.  Could it be?  Are you a....Maximal?"
